    </div>

    <div class="flag-card flag-resolved">
      <div class="flag-header">
        <span class="flag-icon">✅</span>
        <span class="flag-title">Card hover lift: translateY(-3px) → -2px</span>
      </div>
      <p class="flag-body">DS spec defines 2px lift on card hover. Project had 3px. <strong>Decision: reduced to -2px to match DS spec.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="flag-card flag-resolved">
